### lazyReexports {#a8395f3c722c15e6c66c83cf2beb305d7}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>friend std::unique&#95;ptr&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/materializationunit">MaterializationUnit</a> &gt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/lazyreexportsmanager">LazyReexportsManager</a> &amp; LRM, <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/orc/#adfa7bcc2544e48c4531ebfe74ae622b2">SymbolAliasMap</a> Reexports</>}>
Define lazy-reexports based on the given <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/orc/#adfa7bcc2544e48c4531ebfe74ae622b2">SymbolAliasMap</a>.

Each lazy re-export is a callable symbol that will look up and dispatch to the given aliasee on first call. All subsequent calls will go directly to the aliasee.
